OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer James Hockaday
OL,8,FSo-called "forever chemicals" have
OL,9,Fbeen a growing concern in the UK over
OL,10,Ftheir links to cancer and other health
OL,11,Fproblems, and their potential to stay
OL,12,Finside the human body for many years.
OL,14,FPerfluoroalkyl and Polyfluoroalkyl
OL,15,FSubstances (PFAS) are found in such a
OL,16,Fwide range of products that it is hard
OL,17,Fto imagine a world where no one is
OL,18,Fexposed to them, but still, a
OL,19,Fcommittee of MPs has said ministers
OL,20,Fmust do more.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,FOn Thursday, the cross-party
OL,7,FEnvironmental Audit Committee (EAC)
OL,8,Fcalled on the government to restrict
OL,9,Fall non-essential uses of PFAS in
OL,10,Fconsumer products from 2027.
OL,12,FThe calls followed an inquiry into
OL,13,Fforever chemicals, which the committee
OL,14,Fsaid "suggests that our dependence on
OL,15,FPFAs has come with a cost to the
OL,16,Fenvironment, and perhaps to human
OL,17,Fhealth too".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,FPFAs can be found in all sorts of
OL,7,Fitems, including school uniforms,
OL,8,Fwaterproof coats, medicines and non-
OL,9,Fstick frying pans ` but how concerned
OL,10,Fshould people be?
OL,12,FHere, ITV News speaks to experts about
OL,13,Fthe risks and what people can do to
OL,14,Flimit their exposure to these
OL,15,Fpotentially harmful chemicals.
OL,17,FWhat are PFAS?
OL,19,FPFAS are synthetic compounds designed
OL,20,Fto be very stable and robust.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,F"They don't break down very easily,
OL,7,Fhence the term forever chemicals," Dr
OL,8,FLeon Barron, a professor of analytical
OL,9,Fand environmental sciences told ITV
OL,10,FNews.
OL,12,F"They're made to be very heat and
OL,13,Fchemical resistant, but also to confer
OL,14,Fkind of water repellent properties.
OL,16,F"This makes them very useful in a
OL,17,Fnumber of everyday items, some of
OL,18,Fwhich are essential and some of which
OL,19,Fare not essential."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,FPFAS are estimated to account for
OL,7,F15,000 persistent synthetic chemicals
OL,8,Ffound in consumer products, although
OL,9,Fresearchers have suggested the true
OL,10,Fscale of contamination worldwide is
OL,11,Funknown.
OL,13,FWhere are forever chemicals commonly
OL,14,Ffound?
OL,16,FPFAS are commonly associated with non-
OL,17,Fstick cookware, waterproof clothing
OL,18,Fand food packaging, but their use is
OL,19,Fmuch more widespread than one might
OL,20,Fthink.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,FThe compounds are sometimes used in
OL,7,Ftoilet paper, cosmetics, kitchen
OL,8,Ftowels, swimming costumes and even in
OL,9,Fdishwasher tablets.
OL,11,F"There are loads of really tiny
OL,12,Fconveniences that we use them for,"
OL,13,Fsaid Dr David Megson, a reader in
OL,14,Fchemistry and environmental forensics
OL,15,Fat Manchester Metropolitan University.
OL,17,F"I think that if the public had the
OL,18,Fchoice, they'd rather have a soggier
OL,19,Fdish or a soggier towel and minimal
OL,20,Fexposure to a potential carcinogen."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,FWhile PFAS are used for their
OL,7,Fdurability, there's growing evidence
OL,8,Fthat they are entering the UK's
OL,9,Fwaterways and into the environment,
OL,10,Fthe Environment Agency said last year.
OL,12,FPFAS are also used in pesticides,
OL,13,Fwhich the EAC's report said was just
OL,14,Fone way these compounds enter the food
OL,15,Fsystem, with farmers often being
OL,16,Funwittingly exposed to these chemicals
OL,17,Fas they use unlabelled products.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,FThey are also used for certain
OL,7,Fmedicines due to their chemistry and
OL,8,Fdurability, but Dr Megson said this
OL,9,Fwould be considered an essential use
OL,10,Fand wouldn't fall under the scope of
OL,11,Fthe EAC's demands.
OL,13,FWhat are the concerns over PFAS?
OL,15,FAs mentioned above, exposure to some
OL,16,FPFAS is associated with an increased
OL,17,Frisk of developing cancer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,FThey are also linked to changes in the
OL,7,Fimmune system ` reducing the body's
OL,8,Fability to fight infections ` and
OL,9,Fissues related to the reproductive
OL,10,Fsystem.
OL,12,F"Now that obviously depends on how
OL,13,Fmuch of it you're exposed to across
OL,14,Fyour lifetime for any of those things
OL,15,Fto actually manifest," said Dr Barron.
OL,17,FDr Megson said our "convenience-based,
OL,18,Fthrowaway society" is "coming back to
OL,19,Fbite us".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,F"Decades of using these products and
OL,7,Fnot recycling them properly have meant
OL,8,Fthis chemical has been released into
OL,9,Fthe environment," he said.
OL,11,F"It's gone out into the environment;
OL,12,Fit's got into our food chain. And so
OL,13,Fnow we're getting PFAS that were
OL,14,Freleased 30, 40 years ago by our
OL,15,Fparents coming back and exposing us.
OL,17,F"Individually, the products we're
OL,18,Fusing now aren't giving us that much
OL,19,Fexposure. It's relatively minimal. A
OL,20,Fbig issue is the stuff we've released
OL,21,Fyears ago through our negligence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,F"There are bread makers, there are
OL,7,Frice cookers, there's a whole wide
OL,8,Frange of products now that use these
OL,9,Fcompounds for our convenience.
OL,11,F"When you start adding up all of those
OL,12,Fminimal exposures from our convenience
OL,13,Flifestyle, it starts getting quite
OL,14,Fbad."
OL,16,FHow worried should people be and how
OL,17,Fshould they change their habits?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31012
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,FNon-stick frying pans get a lot of the
OL,7,Fblame in the media, but Dr Megson said
OL,8,Fyou will get "much more PFAS exposure
OL,9,Ffrom the food you cook in that frying
OL,10,Fpan than the frying pan itself".
OL,12,F"So, I wouldn't advocate for people to
OL,13,Fgo spending a hundred quid on a brand-
OL,14,Fnew ceramic set.
OL,16,F"So long as you use that pan within
OL,17,Fthe manufacturer's guidelines at
OL,18,Frelatively low temperatures, the PFAS
OL,19,Fthat come off that pan should be low."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31013
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,FDr Megson said he "cringes" at the
OL,7,Fsight of people using metal forks on
OL,8,Ftheir frying pan, which can scrape the
OL,9,Fnon-stick coating off cookware.
OL,11,FHe added that even if a fragment of
OL,12,Fpan coating did go through your body,
OL,13,Fit is "probably going to pass straight
OL,14,Fthrough you", and PFAS exposure should
OL,15,Fbe "minimal".
OL,17,FHowever, he said the best way to
OL,18,Fminimise exposure is to replace your
OL,19,Fnon-stick cookware once it shows signs
OL,20,Fof wear and tear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31014
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,FAs someone who has studied PFAS
OL,7,Fextensively, Dr Barron said he doesn't
OL,8,Fuse PFAS coatings in his frying pans,
OL,9,Fand while his household has an air
OL,10,Ffryer, they try to limit its use.
OL,12,F"Look for the PFAS-free label. You can
OL,13,Fget alternatives almost in every
OL,14,Fshop," he said.
OL,16,FWhile he does not urge people to chuck
OL,17,Ftheir pans and air fryers away, he too
OL,18,Fadvises people to dispose of them once
OL,19,Fthey see "blistering" on the surface
OL,20,Fand to consider not buying PFAS
OL,21,Fproducts moving forward.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31015
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FOffering one small piece of
OL,12,Freassurance, Dr Barron said there is a
OL,13,F"misconception" that our drinking
OL,14,Fwater is "riddled with PFAS".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31016
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,F"We certainly don't find that from our
OL,7,Fresearch," he said. "We have a paper
OL,8,Fcoming out shortly showing that
OL,9,Fcertainly in London, where PFAS
OL,10,Fconcentrations are just a little bit
OL,11,Fhigher, are still below any sort of
OL,12,Frisk threshold for humans.
OL,14,F"So rushing out to buy bottled water
OL,15,Fis not necessarily going to make a
OL,16,Fmassive difference over, you know,
OL,17,Fbuying and generating more plastic
OL,18,Fwaste."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31017
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,FDr Megson said contaminated drinking
OL,7,Fwater is "one of the few areas that is
OL,8,Fwell monitored and regulated to make
OL,9,Fsure our exposure is low", but that so
OL,10,Fmany other sources are not well
OL,11,Fregulated enough to tell the scale of
OL,12,Fthe problem.
OL,14,F"We need to start reducing this with
OL,15,Fstronger legislation and make it
OL,16,Fclearer to consumers if products they
OL,17,Fbuy contain PFAS," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31018
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776974758
OL,3,CPFAS: What are the concerns over
OL,4,C'forever chemicals'?
OL,6,F"I believe the majority of us in the
OL,7,FUK contain PFAS concentrations that
OL,8,Fput us at an increased health risk, we
OL,9,Fneed to reduce our exposure."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/18
